        "section_value": "I will continue the patient's current medication regimen of chlorthalidone. I will increase the metformin dosage to 1500 mg daily. I will recommend a referral to a registered dietitian for dietary counseling to reduce sodium intake. I will also recommend that the patient monitor his blood pressure three times a week at home and provide a blood pressure monitor. I will schedule a follow-up appointment in one month to assess the patient's blood pressure and blood glucose levels and to adjust the treatment plan as needed. I will also schedule a follow-up appointment in one month to assess the patient's blood pressure and blood glucose levels and to adjust the treatment plan as needed.",
